      "line": 12
    },
    {
      "asset": "sbms",
      "type": "translation",
      "language": "en",
      "data": "Showing His mercy, God has revealed Himself unto me."
    },
    {
      "asset": "sbms",
      "type": "translation",
      "language": "pa",
      "data": "ਵਾਹਿਗੁਰੂ ਨੇ ਮਿਹਰ ਧਾਰ ਕੇ ਆਪਣੇ ਆਪ ਨੂੰ ਮੇਰੇ ਤੇ ਜ਼ਾਹਰ ਕੀਤਾ ਹੈ।"
